item.description: Kevin and I did a bit of mentoring yesterday with founders at You Is Now, a startup accelerator run by Scout24 Portals. Scout24 bundles leading digital marketplaces for cars and real estate under one name, the most recognizable for us Berliners being ImmoScout.de. Eywalk and VRnow make up the current class, intentionally smaller than in the past to allow for more focused support from the corporate team.
